thread.title: BRIEF-Trans Genic starts discussion regarding business and capital alliance with BSRC

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Trans Genic starts discussion regarding business and capital alliance with BSRC

organizations.name: public interest incorporated foundation biosafety research center

text:
Jan 18 (Reuters) - Trans Genic Inc
* Says it starts discussion regarding business and capital alliance with Public Interest Incorporated Foundation BioSafety Research Center (BSRC)
* Says it will set up a wholly owned unit, to take over CRO business from BSRC
* Others details not disclosed
Source text in Japanese: goo.gl/iUu8uX
